This code is compiling on Linux and Mac with f77 lapack, cblas, fftw3,
and the unwrap (included) libraries linking.

For Linux, change the cblas.h include in "ops.h" to <atlas/cblas.h>

To compile libunwrap:
cd punwrap
gcc -c <all-c-files> -O
ar -rv libunwrap.a *.o
ranlib libunwrap.a
cd ..

To compile recon:
gcc -g -o recon recon.c image.c data.c bpc.c geo_undist.c -L./punwrap \
    -L/usr/lib/atlas (if stuff isn't sym-linked to /usr/lib) \
    -lm -lfftw3 -lunwrap -lcblas -llapack

